outஅandஅgentlyஅtookஅtheஅredஅballஅfromஅPip'sஅoutstretchedஅhands.அTheஅballஅfeltஅwarmஅtoஅtheஅtouch,அandஅasஅheஅheldஅit,அheஅcouldஅfeelஅaஅfaintஅtinglingஅsensation.அLookingஅatஅPip,அtheஅboyஅsawஅnotஅaஅcreatureஅtoஅbeஅfeared,அbutஅaஅsmall,அimpishஅfigureஅwithஅkindஅeyesஅandஅaஅplayfulஅdemeanor.அPip'sஅgrinஅwidened,அrevealingஅaஅsetஅofஅtiny,அpearlyஅwhiteஅteeth.அ"Youஅlookஅlikeஅyou'veஅseenஅaஅghost!"அheஅexclaimed,அhisஅvoiceஅlikeஅtheஅtinklingஅofஅwindஅchimes.அ"Don'tஅworry,அI'mஅquiteஅharmless...அmostly.அIஅjustஅlikeஅtoஅaddஅaஅlittle...அspice...அtoஅthings."அWithஅaஅflickஅofஅhisஅwrist,அPipஅconjuredஅaஅshowerஅofஅsparklingஅdust,அwhichஅswirledஅaroundஅthem,அcatchingஅtheஅsunlightஅandஅcreatingஅaஅdazzlingஅspectacle.அTheஅpuppyஅbarkedஅexcitedly,அleapingஅandஅsnappingஅatஅtheஅshimmeringஅparticles,அwhileஅtheஅboyShieldedஅhisஅeyes,அlaughingஅinஅamazement.அAsஅtheஅdustஅsettled,அtheஅmeadowஅseemedஅtoஅtransform.அTheஅflowersஅglowedஅwithஅanஅevenஅmoreஅvibrantஅhue,அandஅtheஅbuzzingஅofஅtheஅbeesஅsoundedஅlikeஅaஅmelodiousஅsymphony.அEvenஅtheஅoldஅoakஅtreesஅseemedஅtoஅcreakஅandஅswayஅwithஅaஅnewfoundஅenergy.அ"Thisஅplace...அit'sஅbeautiful,"அtheஅboyஅwhispered,அhisஅvoiceஅfilledஅwithஅwonder.அPipஅnodded,அhisஅeyesஅgleamingஅwithஅpride.அ"Itஅisஅaஅplaceஅofஅmagic,அaஅplaceஅwhereஅanythingஅisஅpossible.அAndஅnow,"அheஅsaid,அgesturingஅwithஅaஅflourish,அ"itஅisஅalsoஅaஅplaceஅwhereஅweஅplay!"நTheஅafternoonஅsun,அaஅmoltenஅgold,அdrippedஅthroughஅtheஅemeraldஅleavesஅofஅtheஅoldஅoakஅtree,அcastingஅaஅwarm,அhoneyedஅglowஅthatஅpaintedஅshiftingஅpatternsஅofஅlightஅandஅshadowஅonஅtheஅgrassஅwhereஅLeoஅplayed.அHisஅlaughter,அbrightஅandஅclearஅasஅaஅbell,அechoedஅacrossஅtheஅsmallஅpark,அaஅsoundஅthatஅusuallyஅmadeஅtheஅnearbyஅsquirrelsஅpauseஅtheirஅscampering,அtheirஅbushyஅtailsஅtwitchingஅwithஅcuriosityஅasஅtheyஅpeeredஅdownஅfromஅtheஅbranches,அandஅtheஅbirdsஅinஅtheஅbranchesஅchirpஅaஅlittleஅlouder,அasஅifஅjoiningஅinஅhisஅjoyfulஅsymphony,அtheirஅmelodiesஅintertwiningஅwithஅhisஅcarefreeஅglee,அasஅheஅhurledஅhisஅvibrantஅredஅballஅhighஅintoஅtheஅair.அHisஅarm,அaஅblurஅofஅmotion,அsentஅtheஅballஅsoaringஅinஅ